1
00:00:00,219 --> 00:00:08,915
Floor-Plan Studio. Open the seeded property, or upload any floor plan for AI vision ingestion.

2
00:00:08,915 --> 00:00:19,010
The plan is a live shape object — every room and wall is selectable. The rent story: nine hundred a week baseline, twelve-sixty proposed.

3
00:00:19,010 --> 00:00:27,043
Delta view — a computed geometry diff. Red removed, green added, amber modified.

4
00:00:27,043 --> 00:00:36,895
Versions are immutable. Version zero is the original; every change is a git-style hunk with rent impact and compliance flags.

5
00:00:36,895 --> 00:00:44,881
Select the store room, then shift-click a wall. Drag the handles to pick an exact chunk.

6
00:00:44,881 --> 00:00:53,793
One comment covers both targets: make it a study, and cut a servery window. Changes queue locally.

7
00:00:53,793 --> 00:01:03,144
Send. The DeepSeek agent replies with typed, validated geometry operations — the building envelope can never grow.

8
00:01:03,144 --> 00:01:12,872
The new version arrives live: the study, the servery window, and a fresh rent estimate.

9
00:01:12,872 --> 00:01:23,490
Every line in the new hunk traces to a geometry object. Export any version as a styled plan or summary.

10
00:01:23,490 --> 00:01:29,954
Select, comment, send. The agent edits geometry — never pixels.
